Introduction

This is a smart report generated with R on the date 15 September 2023. We used a dataset in the MLDataR called Heart Disease. In this report we will combite what we have learnt so far in the R course.

Methods

We created a logistic regression model

\[ E(Y_i) = \beta_0 + \beta_{1} AGE_i + \beta_{2} SEX_i + \beta_{3} BP_i + \beta_{4} CHOL_i + \epsilon_i\]
